{"tid":1699653,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Mike Pence線人:「撐香港」美國議員將出大招，力推香港法案","createTime":"2019-11-08T06:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T10:10:20.000Z","uid":134071,"like":270,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"156a1b24cafa52eb94478b02dbfcdbdb4e4e4d43","tid":1699653,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:04:16.000Z","msg":"Mark Simon-共和黨黨員， 黎智英助手， 最近更協助安排黎智英會見美國副總統Mike Pence。<br />\n<br />\n而家， Mark Simon話「撐香港」既美國議員們將出大招，力推香港法案在參議院大會審議。<br />\n中美貿易談判形勢明朗，亦有助推動香港法案在參議院大會審議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://mobile.twitter.com/HKMarkSimon/status/1192632039507288065\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FHKMarkSimon%2Fstatus%2F1192632039507288065&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUphbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=c19c366c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://mobile.twitter.com/HKMarkSimon/status/1192632039507288065</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/XLr5chk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXLr5chk.jpg&h=2945a531&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c9bc10912c6bd3f79fd4a44fc5b3d201f4f1dd7","tid":1699653,"uid":41458,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:05:22.000Z","msg":"快啦，頂唔撚住啦<br />\n我要攬炒"},{"pid":"a6c71f4ad39daa67e937a410c5c761d7877a13cf","tid":1699653,"uid":134071,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20190906/china-hong-kong-protests/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fchina%2F20190906%2Fchina-hong-kong-protests%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUphbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=136e438f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20190906/china-hong-kong-protests/zh-hant/</a><br />\n<br />\n其中一個引起注意的面孔是香港傳媒大亨<strong>黎智英(Jimmy Lai)的高級助手馬克&middot;西蒙(Mark Simon)</strong>，大陸對黎智英厭惡至極。<strong>西蒙曾在美國海軍服役，今年7月，他幫助安排了黎智英與副總統彭斯的見面，</strong>引發了中國的正式外交抗議。"},{"pid":"a1db92a233c542749acb131414babfb24a7348ad","tid":1699653,"uid":301989,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:06:10.000Z","msg":"唉都講左幾個月 靠自己算啦"},{"pid":"73c9fbb46e9e43c0a743997daa28e70356c7adcf","tid":1699653,"uid":146285,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:06:38.000Z","msg":"次次都話就黎，結果就係仲未黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384318297d61bcf2f653a225c2a46811068b1870","tid":1699653,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:07:02.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"120d881251281f03b3b75c148036b92e7fc1daf1","tid":1699653,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Mark Simon-共和黨黨員， 黎智英助手， 最近更協助安排黎智英會見美國副總統Mike Pence。<br />\n<br />\n而家， Mark Simon話「撐香港」既美國議員們將出大招，力推香港法案在參議院大會審議。<br />\n中美貿易談判形勢<strong>不明朗</strong>，亦有助推動香港法案在參議院大會審議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://mobile.twitter.com/HKMarkSimon/status/1192632039507288065\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FHKMarkSimon%2Fstatus%2F1192632039507288065&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUphbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=c19c366c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://mobile.twitter.com/HKMarkSimon/status/1192632039507288065</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/XLr5chk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXLr5chk.jpg&h=2945a531&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n更正：中美貿易談判形勢<strong>不明朗</strong>，亦有助推動香港法案在參議院大會審議"},{"pid":"c5205babb5f1f3ce9fc3ce05261212a3cd2d5107","tid":1699653,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:07:42.000Z","msg":"左膠侵投共，不了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxeN9ge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna